OL,3,CNewborn baby died after nurse mum left
OL,4,Chim unattended to go to work
OL,6,FA nurse who left her 10-week-old baby
OL,7,Fhome alone while she went to work has
OL,8,Fbeen jailed.
OL,10,FRuth Auta, 28, tried to persuade her
OL,11,Fchildminder to lie to police to cover
OL,12,Fher tracks when she returned after an
OL,13,Feight hour shift at Royal Bolton
OL,14,FHospital to find Joshua Akerele not
OL,15,Fbreathing.
OL,17,FShe called for an ambulance, but
OL,18,Fdespite attempts to resuscitate him he
OL,19,Fdied just over an hour later, on 20
OL,20,FDecember 2022.
