OL,3,CNewborn baby died after nurse mum left
OL,4,Chim unattended to go to work
OL,6,FAfter being arrested and bailed Auta
OL,7,Fwas arrested once more as she
OL,8,Fattempted to flee the country, booking
OL,9,Fa one-way ticket to Nigeria.
OL,11,FBolton Crown Court heard although
OL,12,Fexperts could not confirm Joshua's
OL,13,Fcause of death, he was a health baby
OL,14,Fand may have overheated due to the
OL,15,Flayers of clothing and bedding he was
OL,16,Fwrapped in.
OL,18,FBut, other potential causes of death
OL,19,Fcould not be ruled out.
