OL,3,CNewborn baby died after nurse mum left
OL,4,Chim unattended to go to work
OL,6,FThe court was told Auta initially told
OL,7,Fpolice she had collected Joshua from a
OL,8,Fchildminder after she had finish work
OL,9,Fbefore taking him home, feeding him
OL,10,Fand placing him on her bed.
OL,12,FShe then claimed to have fallen asleep
OL,13,Fnext to him, waking up to find him
OL,14,Funresponsive.
OL,16,FTo cover herself Auta even sent text
OL,17,Fmessages to the childminder asking her
OL,18,Fto lie to police that she had looked
OL,19,Fafter the 10-week-old that day.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
