OL,4,Chim unattended to go to work
OL,6,FBut the childminder told officers she
OL,7,Fhad not seen Joshua for a few days.
OL,9,FIn her police interview, Auta gave no
OL,10,Fcomment to the questions asked, the
OL,11,Fcourt heard.
OL,13,FPolice seized CCTV footage showing
OL,14,FAuta leaving her flat, at the nurses
OL,15,Faccommodation, at 6.47am without her
OL,16,Fbaby and returning home alone at
OL,17,F3.13pm.
OL,19,FAt 3.24pm Auta called for an
OL,20,Fambulance, with Joshua declared dead
OL,21,Fat 4.40pm.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
