OL,3,CNewborn baby died after nurse mum left
OL,4,Chim unattended to go to work
OL,6,FAuta was charged with cruelty to a
OL,7,Fchild and pleaded guilty at Manchester
OL,8,FMagistrates' court on 24 May 2024,
OL,9,Fwith her case adjourned by a month for
OL,10,Fsentence.
OL,12,FBut, on 6 June 2024, Auta was arrested
OL,13,Fat Gatwick Airport whilst attempting
OL,14,Fto board a flight to Nigeria. She had
OL,15,Fpurchased a one-way ticket.
OL,17,FAuta was sentenced to three years in
OL,18,Fjail when she appeared at Bolton Crown
OL,19,FCourt on 10 September.
