OL,3,CNewborn baby died after nurse mum left
OL,4,Chim unattended to go to work
OL,6,FSara Davie, District Crown Prosecutor
OL,7,Ffor CPS North West said: "Whilst she
OL,8,Fwent to work to provide care for other
OL,9,Fpeople, Ruth Auta left the very person
OL,10,Fwho needed her care the most home
OL,11,Falone.
OL,13,F"As a nurse she should have known the
OL,14,Fdangers of leaving her baby unattended.
OL,16,F"As she begins her sentence, she must
OL,17,Fnow live with the consequences of the
OL,18,Fterrible decision she made that day.
