OL,6,F"Auta has failed to show remorse
OL,7,Fthroughout the case; she misled police
OL,8,Fabout her childcare arrangements and
OL,9,Fthen tried to evade justice by
OL,10,Fattempting to flee the country.
OL,12,F"Our thoughts and sympathies are with
OL,13,Fall those who been affected by
OL,14,FJoshua's death."
